social_posts.post_text:
Looking for a Dominican restaurant that brings all the feels and flavors, @abbabargrill is definitely worth a visit. The music, hookah, and food deliciously prepared by @chef_ronald_santos makes this lowkey lounge an all around vibe. 

Food: 
Picadera (shared/for 2) 
Bang Bang Shrimp 
Chicken Pasta 
Churrasco 
Fried Chicken Basket

Drinks: 
Blue Hawaiian 
Henny Colada 
Casamigos Margarita 

Dessert: 
Tres Leche 
Churros w/ Chocolate Dip 

Let us know if you visit! We’ll def be back soon.
.
.
.
#nycfood #nycfoodie #nycrestaurants #nyceats #dominican #dominicanfood

Are we the only ones obsessed with Thai food? We found this hidden gem @thaisocial_nyc in Queens and it was so good we had to visit twice 🫣 Service, drinks, food, and atmosphere all a 10/10 vibe.  Literally all hits, no misses! 

Our Favs: 

Food:
Calamari 
Chicken Satay Bunny Bun
Wings
Beef Short Rib Panang
Drunken Noodle
Chicken Cashew 

Drinks: 
Lychee Martini
Passionfruit Mojito
Pom Pom Frose
Thai Social Club 

We will def be back for more. Let us know your thoughts if you visit! #thaifood #nycrestaurants #thairestaurant #nycfood #nycfoodie #nycfoodgals

As we enter our grown women era, we live for the things we love in elevated environments. So if you’re telling us we can eat lamb chops while smoking hookah with a choice to dine outdoors this summer, def count us in ! @wisebargrill is an upscale hookah lounge/restaurant offers music and entertainment with a featured party on the weekends, delicious food, amazing drinks, and exotic hookah flavors. This place bought all the vibes we need at our grown age !

We will def be returning and suggest you stop by too! #hookahlounge #hookahnyc #brooklyn #nyceats #nycfood #nycfoodie #brooklynrestaurant #nyclounges #nycparty

If you don’t love a chopped cheese, are you from New York even? We were looking for a chill vibe and stopped by @thelocal_fh to try their loaded chopped cheese and it didn’t disappoint! This cool neighborhood deli also has over 200 beers to select from, but if you’re not a beer fan, check out their selection of wine, ciders, and capri sun cocktails. They offer outdoor and indoor seating with TVs playing sports games. 

Our Favs: 
Loaded Chopped Cheese
Philly Cheesesteak Eggrolls
Loaded Tots
Truffle Mushroom Swiss Burger

They have happy hour specials on weekdays 3pm-7pm. We’ll def be back for more. Let us know if you stop by!
.
.
.
#nyceats #nycdeli #nycbeer #nycfoodie #nycrestaurants #choppedcheese #nyc #nyccheatday #cheatday #cheatdayeats #queensny

In honor of Juneteenth and our people, here are some of our favorite black owned restaurants. Let us know your favs! 
.
.
. 
#juneteenth #blackowned #blackownedbusiness #nyceats #nyceatstagram #nycfood #nycfoodies #blackownedrestaurant

We decided to visit @r40lic an innovative Argentinian restaurant, which received a Michelin award. The ambiance was definitely a vibe; we loved the open fire kitchen concept. They offer indoor and outdoor patio seating. The drinks were smooth and subtle, a perfect fit for the aesthetics of the restaurant. This was our first time trying Argentinian food and those empanadas were stuffed to capacity and delicious! The rigatoni was also cooked to perfection.

Perfect for date night, girls night, or a solo dinner. Let us know if you plan to visit !
.
.
.
#longislandcity #nyrestaurant #lic #nyceats #nycfood #nycrestaurants #michelinguide #michelin #argentina🇦🇷

Summer is here and that means it’s rooftop season ! We kicked it off @rooftopreds a rooftop vineyard located in the Brooklyn Navy Yard. This is a must visit for summer; the tasting menu and delicious pizza menu was definitely a vibe. The views of the city were immaculate, the service was excellent, the wine was spectacular, and we’ll definitely be back! Perfect for date nights, group/friend dates, or a solo date. 

Here are some tips for a smooth visit: 

1. Make a reservation via the eventbrite link on the website and arrive during your allotted time!
2. The location is slightly hidden for this gem; your entrance tickets come with exact directions on how to find it.There’s also a 5 flight staircase hike to get to the vineyard (no elevators), but it’s def worth it and there will be water waiting for you at the top!
3. Bring a light jacket for cooler days.
4. Our pizza will be delivered to your table from a nearby restaurant. You must call before 7pm to order!
5. Parking is extremely limited! We advise to park nearby and walk.

Friday nights @cafepluslounge mean you never know who’s going to pull up! If you’re looking for drinks, good music, hookah, and calm eats, this spot is def a vibe. Seating is limited so we highly suggest a reservation. They have Taco Tuesday specials and a good happy hour plus free hookah from 5-7pm on Thursdays and Sundays!

Our Favs: 
Food: 
Sweet Chili Wings 
Buffalo Mac & Cheese (10/10!)
Calamari 
Surf&Turf
Drinks:
Island Tiki
Cafe Blue 
Cafe Red

Let us know if you stop by and tell them we sent you!
.
.
.
#nycrestaurants #nycfoodie #brooklynrestaurant #nychookah #nyceats #hookah #hookahlounge #nycfood

Summer is for the rooftop vibes & @highkeyrooftop is one you should definitely stop by. The ambiance is bright and floral, giving garden feels and the views are a nice touch. There are frozen, on the rocks and speciality drinks available such as the Gemini Experience (not pictured). They have live DJs on certain days, bottle service, hookah, & tasty bites. Walk-ins are accepted but we recommend making a reservation if you can. 
.
.
.
#nycfood #nyceats #nycfoodie #nycrestaurants #nyclounges #nyc

If the hookah hits, you can count on us to be there. @loqma.cafe is a hidden gem in Brooklyn with a curated hookah experience and flavorful food. As soon as you walk in, the ambiance sets the vibe. The service was amazing, the meat on every dish was tender and juicy, and even though they serve no alcohol, the drinks were refreshing and a perfect fit for the atmosphere. The hookah master caters your experience and allows you to mix your own choice of flavors while ensuring the hookah pulls your entire visit. There is beautiful outdoor patio seating as well as indoor seating. 

Our Favs :
Gyro Taco Bites ( A MUST!)
Chicken Kebab
Lamb Chops 
Mango Passionfruit Lemonade 
Watermelon Cucumber Lemonade
Crepe Platter 

Everything was a 10/10 so we will def be back for more. Let us know if you plan on stopping by and tell them we sent ya!
.
.
.
#nycfoodie #nycrestaurants #nychookah #hookahloungenyc #turkishfoodnyc #nyceats

All Day Brunch in Atlanta?! @lovejustbrunch is a black owned brunch spot that gave us all the vibes we needed. The food was stellar, the customer service was amazing, and the mimosas hit! 

Our Favs 

Cornbread Waffle Stack (A MUST!) 
Crispy Catfish Sandwich
Shrimp & Grits 
Strawberry Lemonade Mimosa

We highly recommend reservations if you’re planning to visit and note you must arrive on time with your entire party to be seated !

.
.
.
#atleats #atleatsbrunch #atlbrunch #atlanta #atlantabrunch #justbrunchatl #justbrunch #lovejustbrunch #atlfoodie #atlfood #atlantaeats

If you’re looking for a reason to be outside on a weekday, it’s def @luckyscocktail All Day Happy Hour Mondays. This black owned cocktail lounge won us over with the drinks, the small plates, and the classic playlist. They offer indoor and outdoor heated patio seating. 

Our Favs:
Food:
Catfish Strips 
Crab Cakes
Sliders
Truffle Fries

Drinks:
10 of Hearts
Knock on Wood 
Bamboo

They also have a Saturday Link w/ a live DJ from 8pm-12 am and host private events. Let us know if you plan on stopping by and then we sent you!

It’s still rooftop season! We visited @lostinparadiserooftop and the views were top tier. Perfect place to catch views of the city, grab small bar bites, and have a few drinks with friends. The menu is limited, but the views make it worth the visit. We highly suggest making a reservation before your visit.

What We Had: 

Food:
Guacamole 
Beef Empanadas 
Paradise Wings 
Truffle Waffle Fries 
Shrimp Tacos & Carnitas Tacos
Birria Pizza

Drinks:
Strawberry Smash
Berry Bloom

Outside, Outside, Outside. 😍 That’s where we wanna be at all times. This outdoor patio restaurant in Soho is worth a visit this summer to enjoy the weather. @gilligansnyc offers drinks, food and garden oasis vibes for a night out in the city. The drinks and ambiance are definitely the stars of the show. If you like frozen drinks, try their frozen watermelon margarita! We suggest making a reservation through Resy if you can , it definitely gets more crowded at times! 
.
.
.
#nycfood #nycfoodie #nyceats #nycrestaurants

If it’s a rooftop vibe, count us in! We decided to try @sonoskyct located on top of the Residence Inn in Norwalk, CT and escape the madness of the city. We got good drinks and light bites while enjoying great views. The food wasn’t our favorite, but we would absolutely stop by again for the drinks and views! Parking was easy, reservations weren’t needed, and service was fast. 

Let us know if you plan on stopping by. 
.
.
.
#ctfoodie #norwalkrestaurants #sono #rooftopbar #ctlocal #connecticutlife #ctfood #ctfoodblogger #ctfoodlovers #rooftop #southnorwalk

Can’t pronounce charcuterie but something these boards just hit! We tried this Big Belly Brunch Board @flava2lounge and got a little taste of everything from our list of brunch favorites. Deviled eggs with oxtail is the combo we didn’t know we needed. The jumbo glass of rum punch and frozen fishbowl were the perfect balance of strong and sweet. Playlist varied from reggae, hip hop, to old school R&B. Hookah is only offered in the outdoor seating area. There is a 90 minute seating limit and the brunch board does take a little longer to come out than other menu items.
.
.
.
#nycbrunch  #bkbrunch #nyceatstagram #nyceating #brunch #brunchtime #nyc #brooklynbrunch

We’re having a warm girl summer, but still wanna go out and catch a vibe. We decided to stop by one of our favorite spots @d_gardenbk for drinks, food, and vibes and it didn’t disappoint! This garden themed outdoor space is perfect for birthdays, girls’ night out, and a lit date night. 

Our Favs: 
Hookah
Food 10/10 ( The Chef deserves an award !)
Frozen Drinks
The Music & Vibes>>
Outdoor & Indoor Seating

Something about jerk chicken fresh off the grill  just does it for us! Every Friday until Labor Day @ccemjerkfridayz hosts their summertime pop up jerk sale from 12-11pm. The authentic food, fresh juices, and rum punch gave us island vibes, but right at home. They offer outdoor seating and fun games you can enjoy during your visit. 

They also offer other menu items, including soup, fish, and grilled corn. Let us know if you stop by this summer! 
.
.
.
#jerkfridayz #jerkchickennyc #nycfood #popup #jerkchicken #jerk #jerkpork #brooklyn #islandfood #foodie

A spot with good food and a nice playlist is always a vibe. @vesselbarandgrill is a bar and grill in downtown Brooklyn with multiple screens playing your favorite sports games, happy hour specials, filling entrees & attentive service. The playlist consisted of classic and current hip-hop and R&B. It’s a good spot for solo drinks at the bar, a date night or group outing. 
.
.
.
.
#nycfood #nyceats #nycrestaurants #nycfoodie #brooklyn

We’re in our creative girl era and wanted to try something different. We stopped by @paintnpourinc in Harlem and had the time of our lives. The playlist, the all night open bar, and our amazing instructor, Scott brought alll the vibes ! We said we were only having a “few” drinks, but several drinks later, we were giving starving artists vibes.  We decided to try the small bites available to order. They offer both indoor and outdoor studio classes. You can follow along with the instructions or freestyle your masterpiece, which we loved!

They also offer Brush N Blaze classes(420 Friendly) that comes with a complimentary pre roll! Tickets are available for purchase on their website and seating is limited so we highly suggest you schedule in advance. 
.
.
.
#paintnpournyc #paintandsip #paintandsipnyc #nycthingstodo #nycfun #harlem #harlemnyc #paintnpour #nycoutdoordining #nycfoodie

You know if Mayor Adams visited a spot, it was automatically a vibe. @izakayanana transports you to the heart of Japan, landing you in this Tokyo style alleyway full of surprises. The interior decorations, private rooms, culinary artwork created the ultimate dining experience. The staff was friendly and ready with menu suggestions. This spot is perfect for date night, group meet ups, or family dinners. 
.
.
.
#queensnyc #izakayanana #queensrestaurant #japanesefood #sakebar #nycfood #nyceats #nycfoodie #queensny #nycjapanesefood #cheatdayeats #ericadams

There’s something about a garden patio that makes us feel like we’re summering right ! @room100bk inspired by the Prohibiton Era gave speakeasy, but in the middle of Brooklyn. The food was amazing, the hookah was smooth, and the drinks looked and tasted good. We ended our night walking to their hidden garden patio, where the vibes continued! 

What We Had :
Room 1 Hundred Wings 
Philly Cheesesteak Eggrolls  Tempura Shrimp Bites

Crispy Skin Salmon
Lobster Mac & Cheese 
Colorado Lamb Chops 

Natillini
Ume Pornstar
Como Una Flor
Tropical Paradise

Let us know if you visit and tell them we sent ya!
.
.
.

#room100bk #brooklyn #nyceats #nycfoodie #nycfood #nycrestaurants #brooklyneats #brooklynfoodie #queens #queenseats #queensfood #nychookah #nycgarden #nycdrinks #nyccocktails #nycbrunch

There is just something about the hookah at Mediterranean restaurants that we absolutely love. We decided to try @knifeatl for a late birthday celebration and truly tapped into our grown women era. The dress code solidified that it was time to give grown and sexy. The juicy lamb and chicken kebabs were tender and marinated perfectly, but those Brussel sprouts stole the show. The drinks presentation was beautiful, but the drinks still delivered on taste and strength. The service was excellent. The decor is beautiful with multiple opportunities for pictures. Perfect for birthdays, anniversaries, or special occasions.

They have a live DJ who played a mix of r&b and trending songs. They offer brunch every Sunday from 12pm-3pm. There is a fee for parking.
.
.
.
#knifeatl #atlanta #druski #atlantaeats #atlfoodie #atlfood #atlrestaurants #atlhookah #atlhookahlounges #atlfoodblogger #atlantafood #atlantarestaurants #atlantarestaurant #atlantafood #atlantahookahlounge #atlantahookah #knifeatlanta

There’s a new spot in town and we would fight for this chef like it was the Montgomery brawl! @velvetroombk just opened up and is already in our top 5 spots of the summer. The food was just as good as it looks, the bartender delivered all night, the hookah was smooth, and the playlist was fire! The service was excellent. 

You should put this at the top of your list of spots to try; we know we will def be back ! 
.
.
.
#brooklynrestaurants #velvetroombk #nyceats #blackownedrestaurant #nycfood #nycfoodie #brooklynfood #brooklynfoodie #brooklyneats #nycrestaurants #nycrestaurant #nycfoodgals #queensfoodie #queensfood

A private hibachi experience with endless sake, @hibachiomakase brought the vibes right to our backyard. We each enjoyed a starter salad and then had the option of 2 proteins paired with fried rice and veggies. Of course, they brought the perfect sauces to pair with each part of our  meals. Our chef kept us entertained the entire night and def elevated our experience.

Perfect for hosting group celebrations right at home with services available across the country. Pricing details available on their website. 
.
.
.
#hibachiomakase #backyardhibachi #sake #hibachiathome #hibachi #hibachicatering #nyccatering #nycevents #hibachigrill #hibachinyc

Dressing up and going out to eat is our favorite love language. @theconsulatemidtown is a French inspired brasserie that gave us aesthetics and fine dining. We sat on the second level and got to take fire pictures on that winding staircase leading to the upper level of dining. Our food and drinks matched the classy vibes that the restaurant gave and we had the best service the entire night. Our fav food items were the crab cakes, the shrimp toast, and the branzino. Perfect for girls night, date night, and special occasions. 
.
.
.
#datenightnyc #theconsulate #nycdining #nycdinner #nycfood #nycfinedining #nycrestaurants #nyceats #manhattan #manhattanfood #manhattaneats #nycdrinks #nycdatenight

Sundays are for relaxing and unwinding, but first we brunch! The aesthetics, the refreshing beverages, and the tasty menu options @clavelnyc gave us the perfect solo brunch date vibes. It was literally love at first bite and the quality of everything we tasted was top tier. We will def be back for more!

What We Tried : 
Turkey Club
Chicken Burger 
Stuffed French Toast 
Blue Açaí Bowl
Chicken & Waffle 

Magic Latte
Raspberry Lemonade
Spritz Drink 

Let us know if you stop by and tell them we sent ya! 
.
.
.
#brunchnyc #brunch #nycfood #nyceats #nycbreakfast #nyccoffee #nyccoffeeshops #nycbakery #nycfoodie #brooklyn #brooklynfood #brooklynfoodie #nyclunch #alldaybreakfast #alldaybrunch

If you’re near Grand Central Terminal, you need to head to the Urbanspace Food Court and try @mikeypomodoro. Family recipes, savory sauces, and deliciousness in every bite, this is Italian comfort food at its best. We tried the meatballs, sliders trio, and rice balls and loved everything. These were probably the best meatballs we ever had in NY and that spicy vodka chicken parm slider was to die for ! The way Mikey explained his food to us, we could tell everything was made with love. We ended our meal with the most refreshing homemade lemonade.

There is very limited food court seating available. The service is exceptional and we will def be returning. 
.
.
.
#italianfood #italianfoodnyc #nycitalianfood #nyceats #nycfood #nycfoodie #mikeypomodoro #italianfoodlover #italiancuisine #italianrestaurant #italianfoodbloggers #italianfoodporn #nycrestaurants #grandcentralterminal #urbanspace #grandcentralstation #grandcentral

POV: You feel like you’re in Havana but it’s a Summer Night in New York 💜 @auracocina brings all the decor, food, drinks and live music to give you that vibe plus an Asian fusion twist! The food was well flavored and filling, the drinks were creative and tasty and the vibe is enchanting. The service was also friendly and accommodating. We love it here for a date night, ladies night, or special occasion celebration. Let us know if you stop by! 

We Ordered: 
Kani Crab Empanadas
Red Curry Fried Calamari 

Miso Salmon
Skirt Steak
Shrimp Rice
Yucca Fries 

“El Coco”
Sangria
Mango Margarita 

.
.
.
#nyceats #nycfood #nycrestaurants #nycfoodie #brooklyn #brooklyneats #datenight #date #ladiesnight #birthday

This hidden gem @bar_1_elleven in Brooklyn transported us to someplace magical. The ambiance, the presentation, and the delivery, because the food and drinks were on point, gave us all the vibes! And if it’s a solo date, no worries! The red bears seated with you will keep you plenty of company. The bartender gave technique, engaging presentation, and exquisite cocktails with premium liquor. 

There is indoor and outdoor seating, but we loved the vibe of the outdoor garden. The service was amazing. This is perfect for a lowkey date night, solo night out, or girls’ night. 

Let us know if you visit! 
.
.
.
#foodblogger #foodporn #nycrestaurant #brooklyn #brooklynrestaurant #explorepage #fyp #food #nycbar #nycfoodie #newyorkcity #nycrestaurants #nyceats #nyceeeeeats #nyceeeeats #nyc  #nycfood #nycfoodgals #nycfoodies #nycfoodporn #nycfoodinsta

It’s Wine Wednesdays and we decided to stop by @therapywinebar2.0 for some wine and jazz. We loved their Barbie After Dark charcuterie board that comes with a bottle of wine. They offer $3 mimosas for brunch on the weekends and during the weekdays happy hour. They have a Rise & Rosé special on Saturdays that includes a bottle of Rosé w/ 2 pairs of Pink sunglasses. 

This is the perfect first date, girls night out, or solo date spot. The vibes were calm and relaxing and there was live jazz was playing in background. Def for the grown and sexy! 

Food: 
Oxtail Wontons
Therapy Jerk Wings
Shrimp Wontons
Slider Sampler

Cocktails: 
Rose Gimlet 
F Around & Find Out 
The Blamptons 
Champagne Mojito

Let us know if you plan on stopping by ! 
.
.
.
#therapywinebar #nyceats #nycwine #winetasting #winelover #winestagram #nyccocktails #nycdrinks #tapasbar #nycfoodie #nycfood #nycrestaurants #blackowned #nycbars  #nycbar #nychappyhour #nycbrunch

Date nights, surprises, vacations, and flowers! We went to @prestige_restaurant_lounge for date night and the vibes were immaculate. The food was delicious, the DJ played the tunes all night, the hookah was hookahin’, and the drinks were strong and pretty. This the perfect spot for date night, birthday celebrations, anniversary dinners, or special occasions. They have indoor and outdoor seating with multiple walls for photo opps. The service was amazing and we will def we back ! 

What We Tried :
Wings 💜
Calamari 💜
Lamb Chops 💜💜
Surf & Turf 💜💜💜 
Oysters 💜💜💜
Carrot Cake 💜💜💜
.
.
.
#nycrestaurant #nycsteakhouse #nyceats #nycfood #nycfoodie #nycfoodies #brooklyn #bkeats #brooklynrestaurant #brooklynfoodie #datenight #datenightnyc #nycbirthday #nycdinner #nyclounges #nychookah

Burgers, drink towers, hookah, and views! @fultonburgerbk gave us the after work pick me up we needed. Their mouth watering specialty burgers and buttermilk chicken sandwich for our non-red meat tribe left us in foodie heaven. The passion fruit margarita tower is strong, but good! It’s $65 during happy hour along with their other cocktail specials for under $10. And if you need more comfort food vibes, they had some fire mozzarella sticks and buffalo wings.

They offer hookah on the outside patio area. There is indoor and outdoor seating available. The views of the Brooklyn Bridge from this location are immaculate. Perfect for after work comfort vibes, meet up with friends, or a solo date.
.
.
.
#nychappyhour #dumbo #dumbobrooklyn #brooklynbridge #brooklyn #brooklynbar #nycrestaurants #nycfood #nycfoodie #nyceats #brooklyneats #brooklynfood #brooklynfoodie #nyccocktails #nycdrinks

Guys, the wine was winin’ and we’re still tore up from the Generous Pour at Capital Grille! This deal gives you 7 tasting glasses of wines varying from rose to whites to reds and 2 pours of your fav tasting. Some locations allow purchase of an appetizer, however, our waiter made it very clear that we must purchase an entree. The deal ends 9/3 but reservations are readily available so grab your crew and head on over NOW !

Please have a designated driver y’all; It’s Labor Day weekend!! 

Let us know if you have tried this deal and what your experience was in the comments !
.
.
.
#thegenerouspour #capitalgrille #winetasting #winetime #winetastings #winelover #winestagram #wine #winelovers #steak #steakhouse #thecapitalgrille #nycrestaurants #nycdrinks #nycfood #nycfoodie #nyceats #nycnightlife

New York City is epitome of for the culture. We recently stopped by the first Albanian restaurant in the city and tried some different eats while being surrounded by art and history. It’s giving transport us to a different country every week. The drinks were immaculate and the bread and dip combo plus the grilled meat platter won us over. There is indoor and outdoor seating available. The servers were informative about the food choices and helped us find our perfect matches. If you’re looking for something outside of your comfort zone, we recommend you stop by @ckakaqellu.
.
.
.
#nycrestaurants #albania #albanianfood #nyceats #nycfood #nycfood #ctfoodie #bronxfood #nyc #nycdining #nycdinner #nycdrinks #nycfoodie

We were craving Chinese food, but still wanted a vibe so we stopped by the Grand Street location of @3timesnyc and it is officially our new fav dim sum spot! The playlist was fire so we were eating, drinking, and dancing the whole night. The drinks were strong but tasty. Our waiter suggested we try some traditional food and mix them with our fav typical dishes and everything was 10/10. 

Our Favs 🥟🍜🍸
Pork Soup Dumplings 
Double Cooked Pork Belly 
General Tso’s Chicken
Sweet and Spicy Wings 
Hong Kong Style Fried Rice 

Lychee Martini
Floral Drink 

Let us know if you stop by! 
.
.
.
#nycrestaurant #dimsum #chinesefood #nycfood #nyc #nyceats #nycfoodie #nycdrinks #brooklyn #brooklyneats #brooklynfood #brooklynfoodie #nycrestaurants #authentic

We heard September is take a man on a date month and we wanted to try something a little different. We may be creators, but we’re not always creative so we called on @suitelifestudios to set up this luxurious picnic in the park for date night. They executed this experience so perfectly from the games to keep us entertained, the fans to cool us down, and perfect canvas to paint on. 

We know the weather is changing soon, but don’t worry they offer indoor picnic services, hotel room decorating services, and can curate an experience for up to 12 guests. 

Check out their page to book your luxury picnic or room experience! Let us know if you’ll be taking your a man on a date this month. 
.
.
.
#picnic #picnicdate #nycdecorator #nycdecor #nycluxury #nycthingstodo #brooklynbridge #nycpark #astoria #astoriaqueens #astoriapark #nycdatenight #nycdating #nycdateideas #datenight #dateideas #nycpartyplanner #nyceventplanner #nycevents #nyceventdesigner #blackgirlluxury #blackgirlswhoblog #luxurypicnic #luxurypicnics #luxurylifestyle #luxurydesign #luxurypicnicplanner

One thing about the uptown spots is the vibes are there year round! We went to this Dominican sushi spot @sushimambony, but unfortunately weren’t able to try the sushi because of our later dining time. The appetizers weren’t as seasoned as we would’ve liked, but our entrees were 10/10. We had the land and sea entree and the ribeye with a special fried rice. The drinks were strong and good; our favs were the lychee martini and the casamigos margarita. The tres leche cake was one of most unique but tastiest ones we have ever had. The music was mostly Latin with a mix of some hip hop/rnb. There was indoor and outdoor seating available. 

The service was kind of disappointing and not as welcoming as we would have liked, which sometimes can be typical of uptown spots if we’re being honest. Hopefully, this has been corrected as our visit was a while back. 

Let us know if you have ever tried Dominican sushi in the comments!
.
.
.
#uptownnyc #nycfood #nycrestaurants #nycfoods #nycfoodies #nycfoodgals #nycfoodblogger #nycfoodporn #nychookah #dyckman #harlem #harlemfood #nycrestaurant #nycadventures #nyceats #nycsushi #dominicanfood

Night time views of NYC from a rooftop bar & lounge >>> @monarchnyc is an indoor/outdoor rooftop lounge in the sky with unbeatable views of the city. They serve drinks with clever names like “Don’t be Salty” & “Hits Different” as well as small plates. The service was okay and the music was more like background music but the views and drinks make the vibe. You can walk in and go to the bar or reserve seating which we recommend. It’s a good after or before dinner spot, day date, ladies link up or small group outing. Stop by & enjoy this fall weather from above! 

Featured:
•Shrimp Dumplings
•Lobster Roll Sliders
•Frose
•Mango Margarita 
•”Extra AF”
•”Don’t be Salty”
